'''Muteki wa mahungu''' i munhu loyi a hlengeletaka, a tsala, kumbe a haxa mahungu kumbe timhaka leti endlekaka sweswinyana. Muteki wa mahungu anga tirhana na tin'wana na tin'wana kumbe a lavisisa timhaka to karhi hi ku kongoma. Hambiswiritano vateki va mahungu votala va rhandza ku hlawulekisa swiyenge swa mahungu leswi va tirhanaka na swona, ivi va tirhisana na van'wana ku kandziyisa maphephahungu lawa ma khumbaka timhaka to hambanahambana. Hixikombiso, muteki wa mahungu ya tamintlangu, u tsala no haxa hi tamintlangu ntsena hambi leswi angava a thoriwe hi bindzu ra phephahungu leri khumbaka ti mhaka to hamabanahambana.
